WEBVTT

00:10:58.542 --> 00:11:00.101
who explained her job to me.

00:11:00.125 --> 00:11:02.268
She said that she checks in on clients,

00:11:02.292 --> 00:11:04.226
checks their vital signs,

00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:05.726
takes them grocery shopping,

00:11:05.750 --> 00:11:07.042
goes on long walks,

00:11:08.125 --> 00:11:09.583
has conversations.

00:11:10.917 --> 00:11:14.208
She told me, "I let them know
somebody has their back."

00:11:15.583 --> 00:11:17.583
And the results have been astounding.

00:11:18.625 --> 00:11:21.809
Patients are healthier,
hospitals less burdened.

00:11:21.833 --> 00:11:23.309
As for Destini,

00:11:23.333 --> 00:11:26.542
she tells me her family
and she are healthier.

00:11:27.625 --> 00:11:32.875
"And," she adds, "I love that I get
to contribute to my community."